<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Chukwunonso Onovo — Data Scientist & Engineer</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter+Tight:wght@600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="site.css" />
  <style>
    
    :root {
      --bg: #F5F3EE;
      --bg2: #EDEAE3;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --surface2: #F9F7F4;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --border-strong: rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
      --text-1: #1A1814;
      --text-2: #4A4640;
      --text-3: #8A8480;
      --accent: #4A80D4;
      --accent-light: rgba(74,128,212,0.22);
      --accent-dim: rgba(74,128,212,0.08);
      --tag-bg: #EDE9E3;
      --tag-text: #4A4640;
      --nav-bg: rgba(245,243,238,0.88);
      --serif: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      --sans: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      --heading: 'Inter Tight', sans-serif;
      --radius: 16px;
      --transition: 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: #131210;
      --bg2: #1C1A17;
      --surface: #211F1B;
      --surface2: #2A2722;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
      --text-1: #F0EDE6;
      --text-2: #B8B0A4;
      --text-3: #6B6560;
      --accent: #6B9FE4;
      --accent-light: rgba(107,159,228,0.22);
      --accent-dim: rgba(107,159,228,0.08);
      --tag-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --tag-text: #B8B0A4;
      --nav-bg: rgba(19,18,16,0.9);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--sans);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-1);
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
    }

    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      background: var(--nav-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      height: 60px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      transition: background var(--transition);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-center {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-center a {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--text-3);
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-center a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .theme-toggle {
      width: 40px; height: 22px;
      background: var(--surface2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      border-radius: 100px;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
      transition: background var(--transition);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .theme-toggle::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 3px; left: 3px;
      width: 14px; height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle::after {
      transform: translateX(18px);
    }

    .nav-contact {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-contact:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
    }

    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 4px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
    }

    .hamburger span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px; height: 1.5px;
      background: var(--text-2);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      top: 60px; left: 0; right: 0;
      background: var(--nav-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      z-index: 199;
    }

    .mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }

    .mobile-menu a {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-2);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .mobile-menu a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero-section {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 80px 2rem 5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg-text {
      position: absolute;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(80px, 16vw, 220px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--border);
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      white-space: nowrap;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
    }

    .hero-avatar {
      width: 100px; height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      border: 3px solid var(--accent-light);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      
    }

    .hero-name {
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text-1);
    }

    .hero-name .accent { color: var(--accent); }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-3);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      max-width: 480px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .hero-socials {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .social-pill {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-2);
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .social-pill:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-dim);
    }

    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--text-3);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 1px; height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scaleY(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1.15); }
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1140px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .page-section { padding: 6rem 0; }

    .section-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text-1);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-title .accent { color: var(--accent); }

    .section-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      max-width: 1140px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ABOUT */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .about-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text-2);
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .about-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }

    .location-card {
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .location-text {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .location-sub {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      opacity: 0.65;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .skills-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skills-label {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-3);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .skill-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }

    .skill-tag {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.67rem;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      background: var(--tag-bg);
      color: var(--tag-text);
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .skill-tag:hover {
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* PROJECTS */
    .projects-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .project-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: var(--accent-light);
    }

    .project-thumb {
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      background: var(--bg2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }

    .project-thumb-grid {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, var(--border) 0, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 36px),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 0, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 36px);
    }

    .project-thumb-label {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-3);
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .project-num {
      position: absolute; bottom: 1rem; right: 1rem;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--text-3); z-index: 1;
    }

    .project-body {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.85rem; flex: 1;
    }

    .project-header {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;
    }

    .project-title {
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: var(--text-1);
    }

    .project-link-btn {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-3);
      font-size: 0.8rem; flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .project-link-btn:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-dim);
    }

    .project-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

    .project-tag {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      background: var(--tag-bg); color: var(--tag-text);
    }

    .project-desc {
      font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .project-card.add-card {
      border-style: dashed; background: transparent;
    }

    .add-inner {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      min-height: 240px; gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .add-circle {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1.5px dashed var(--border-strong);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-3);
    }

    .add-label {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-3);
    }

    /* EXPERIENCE */
    .exp-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

    .exp-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .exp-item:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

    .exp-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem; padding-top: 0.2rem; }

    .exp-date {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .exp-company {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--text-3); line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .exp-role {
      font-family: var(--heading); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-1); margin-bottom: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .exp-desc {
      font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-2);
      line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .exp-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

    .exp-tag {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.6rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem; border-radius: 100px;
      background: var(--tag-bg); color: var(--tag-text);
    }

    /* EDUCATION */
    .edu-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .edu-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.75rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .edu-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent-light);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .edu-year {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent);
    }

    .edu-degree {
      font-family: var(--heading); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-1); line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .edu-school {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.67rem;
      color: var(--text-3); line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .edu-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 0.2rem 0; }

    .edu-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-name {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem;
       color: var(--text-2);
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .edu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .nav-center, .nav-contact { display: none; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }
      .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .edu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .exp-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 1.75rem 0; }
      .page-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      nav { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      .container { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <span class="nav-logo">C. Onovo</span>
    <ul class="nav-center">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
      <li><a href="#education">Education</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeBtn" aria-label="Toggle dark mode"></button>
      <a href="mailto:placeholder@email.com" class="nav-contact">Contact</a>
      <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Open menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
    <a href="#about" onclick="closeMobile()">About</a>
    <a href="#projects" onclick="closeMobile()">Projects</a>
    <a href="#experience" onclick="closeMobile()">Experience</a>
    <a href="#education" onclick="closeMobile()">Education</a>
    <a href="mailto:placeholder@email.com" onclick="closeMobile()">Contact ↗</a>
  </div>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-bg-text" aria-hidden="true">Data</div>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-badge">Lagos, Nigeria · Open to opportunities</div>
      <div class="hero-avatar">C</div>
      <h1 class="hero-name">Chukwunonso<br/><span class="accent">Onovo</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Data Scientist &amp; Engineer · Founder of Westeros Multiservice<br/>Researcher in Food Security &amp; Agricultural Technology
      </p>
      <div class="hero-socials">
        <a href="#" class="social-pill">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-pill">GitHub</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-pill">Twitter / X</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-pill">Medium</a>
        <a href="mailto:placeholder@email.com" class="social-pill">Email ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      <span>Scroll</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <section class="page-section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">01 — About</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Building at the intersection<br/>of <span class="accent">data</span> &amp; engineering</h2>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;">
          <p class="about-text reveal">
            Chukwunonso is a skilled engineer and founder of Westeros Multiservice — a tech company combining automation and technology for business needs. Proficient in Data Science, machine learning, and cloud technology.
          </p>
          <p class="about-text reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
            Currently building towards becoming a leading solutions expert in business analytics while working on Food Security in Agriculture as a lead researcher and consultant. Writer, web developer, and mechatronics engineer. ALX Professional Foundation certificate holder.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-right">
          <div class="location-card reveal">
            <span style="font-size:1.2rem;">📍</span>
            <div>
              <div class="location-text">Lagos, Nigeria</div>
              <div class="location-sub">West Africa Time (WAT) · UTC+1</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
            <div class="skills-label">Core Skills</div>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
